{
  "stem": "39.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, and as we were so confused, we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a group of prisoners of higher ranks who were ordered, just there, to try to pacify us, to make a little order among us, because we really were so confused.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember they just told that young mothers should give the children to the grandmothers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was no explanation why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So many young women didn't want to part from the kids and give it to the grandmothers, but some did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, later on, we knew perfectly well why-- because the little children and the older people were killed right away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we really didn't know why we were told.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they wanted to help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Again, yelling, form lines of five.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were thousands and thousands of lines of five.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Our line of five was grandmother, my mother, myself, my girlfriend Eva, her mother Helen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's how was our line of five.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then we had to go through a big gate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Above the big gate, it was the inscription saying work makes you free, which was the most cynical lie what one could ever imagine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because, as we found out, we arrived to Auschwitz, and Auschwitz was no working camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Auschwitz was extermination camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Auschwitz was the biggest factory of death what one could ever imagine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the front of the gate was standing a very proper looking SS officer by the name of Dr.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Josef Mengele, known also as Angel of Death, the famous killer of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was just standing there, holding a stick in one hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the lines of five had to pass in front of him through the gate.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
